===Noun===
''a'' '''portable''' (''plural'': '''[[portables]]''')

# A portable [[toilet]]; a self-contained [[outhouse]].
# Any [[temporary]] [[building]] that is portable, especially one located at a school.
# A [[hand-held]] [[electronic]] [[gaming]] device.

